    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This vehicle features the M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) with Drivelogic for seamless torque delivery and an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal kinematic response and corner-exit traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle valve actuators. The hydraulic steering rack remains precise, and the braking system retains excellent bite. Though the finish shows minor road-wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain performance remains exemplary.",
      "price": 34500.0,
